{"tid":1929934,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公院用國產搓手液 醫護即手腫","createTime":"2020-03-17T08:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T09:03:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f58023be478b8fa29a9eeec799ec47e945dba314","tid":1929934,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:42:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200317/3YUQMHPHHMEAMWQMO5RRW24YQU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200317%2F3YUQMHPHHMEAMWQMO5RRW24YQU%2F&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8NTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=1e0caab5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200317%2F3YUQMHPHHMEAMWQMO5RRW24YQU%2F&h=eec44614\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200317/3YUQMHPHHMEAMWQMO5RRW24YQU/</a><br />\n<br />\n公院用國產搓手液 醫護即手腫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200317/large/1584375752_40c4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200317%2Flarge%2F1584375752_40c4.gif&h=eaea9f11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n涉事酒精搓手液聲稱有「WHO Formulation 1」認證，即含乙醇、過氧化氫、甘油等成份，如成份無誤，屬世衞認可搓手液。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】醫院管理局日前被踢爆引入「淘寶」有售、內地製造的抗生素Tazocin後，本報獲悉，包括明愛、東區等多間公院日前突轉用一款廣州生產酒精搓手液。有醫護稱用完後雙手紅腫甚至出紅點，懷疑搓手液引發皮膚過敏反應，但因無替代品可用，敢怒不敢言。東區醫院稱已暫停使用該批搓手液，並向醫管局總辦事處呈報事件。<br />\n<br />\n東區醫院醫護向本報投訴，個別部門病房上周轉用由「廣州雪蝶醫藥科技有限公司」生產、廣州白雲區工場製造的酒精搓手液，部份員工雙手紅腫，個別同事更有紅點，相信是皮膚過敏。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n產品聲稱獲世衞認可<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：28人英國返港不適送院<br />\n<br />\n明愛醫院醫護亦表示有類似情況，據稱該款搓手液聲稱有「WHO Formulation 1」認證，即含乙醇、過氧化氫、甘油等成份，屬世衞認可，最佳使用日期為2021年2月前。該醫護承認單看描述質素應有保證，「呢隻用一兩次就唔掂，之前個幾月日日用（其他產品）都冇事&hellip;&hellip;但又唔可以唔用」。<br />\n<br />\n東區醫院發言人證實事件，但強調沒收到投訴，只得悉搓手液「可能引起部份員工敏感」，院方已暫停使用。醫管局已向產品供應商跟進，並即時使用其他代替品。與上周被揭發引入內地製造的抗生素Tazocin事件不同，局方今次沒發新聞稿交代，亦拒答購入多少支搓手液、花費多少錢、會否全數棄置等。<br />\n<br />\n■記者于健民、王春怡"},{"pid":"f46a21cdd97b474b435f8726968e9ce90872a67a","tid":1929934,"uid":83910,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:44:08.000Z","msg":"果d行街買防疫用品<br />\n見到支那製造即刻放低"},{"pid":"152fb444d783720f55e2384d5b453b2afb583f66","tid":1929934,"uid":83910,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f46a21cdd97b474b435f8726968e9ce90872a67a","tid":1929934,"uid":83910,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:44:08.000Z","msg":"果d行街買防疫用品<br />\n見到支那製造即刻放低"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:45:05.000Z","msg":"寧願買印度喜馬拉雅山牌"},{"pid":"d83e1533a017a73d992af98bdcf352417d1672c9","tid":1929934,"uid":286131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f46a21cdd97b474b435f8726968e9ce90872a67a","tid":1929934,"uid":83910,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:44:08.000Z","msg":"果d行街買防疫用品<br />\n見到支那製造即刻放低"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直接用酒精抹手都爛"},{"pid":"445f9170805d81079d8c19bf0fc8dcbdff40d277","tid":1929934,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:45:53.000Z","msg":"化驗，睇下係咪個 d 物質"},{"pid":"959922933d74a0730eee5818464db162d36f7d70","tid":1929934,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"445f9170805d81079d8c19bf0fc8dcbdff40d277","tid":1929934,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:45:53.000Z","msg":"化驗，睇下係咪個 d 物質"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:48:26.000Z","msg":"甲醛 乙醛?"},{"pid":"35ed34d297087bfca41bf510e8e6714caa96c26b","tid":1929934,"uid":72085,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:49:06.000Z","msg":"見到有WHO Formulation 1仲用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be378106c411fca685d428e4f1f33a41886c04d","tid":1929934,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:56:19.000Z","msg":"報導暫時用「聲稱」<br />\n所以要化驗<br />\n不過比例好似驗唔到"},{"pi